children.text: Located at the top of Bonanza lift, quick service style restaurant with an east coast house of pizza vibe
Bistro style dining experience with a robust wine, craft beer, and cocktail menu. Reservations recommended.
Grab-n-Go breakfast and lunch items located in the Grand Summit Hotel at Canyons Village.
This prime aprs ski beer bar offers 360 views from its unique glass enclosure and massive deck in the heart of Canyons Village.
Red Pine Lodge, located at the top of the Red Pine Gondola, is a quick service style restaurant perfect for families with a wide array of menu options and beers on tap.
Located at the bottom of McConkey's and Pioneer lifts. This historic lodge was built in 1896 and features an elevated quick service menu as well our only on mountain full service bar.

Legacy Cafe is located in the Park City Mountain Village plaza in Legacy Lodge. Quick service style dining offering a wide variety of mountainside favorites from our salad bar to burgers and pizza slices.

Miners Camp, located at the base of Silverlode Lift and Quicksilver Gondola, is a spacious quick service style restaurant offering homestyle favorites to enjoy while watching the game in our PickAxe Pub.
Lookout Cabin, located at the mid station of the Orange Bubble Express, is a full service restaurant offering elevated Rocky Mountain cuisine and full service bar with amazing views of the resort.
Located in the Mountain Village Plaza inside Legacy Lodge, Legends Bar and Grill is the perfect place to have a great lunch or end your day with a hot meal and an expertly poured cocktail.
Proudly serving Lavazza coffee and espresso, with a full selection of hot and iced drinks. Grab a latte for the lift, or lunch for later from the Grab N' Go items offered throughout the day.
Located at the top of Dreamscape and Dreamcatcher lifts, this quick service restaurant offers fresh homemade donuts every morning and delicious flatbreads as well as traditional favorites.
Tombstone BBQ, located at the base of the Tombstone and Timberline lifts, features in house smoked BBQ favorites to enjoy on its scenic ski beach.
Sun Lodge, located at the base of the Sunpeak lift, is a southwestern taqueria featuring delicious tacos, burritos, and quesadillas
